    source xplanet/xplanet-$VERSION.tar.gz
  homepage http://xplanet.sourceforge.net
  estimate 150
      desc 'xplanet draws earth or other planets with user-supplied maps.
It renders the image in the root window or an X window.
Azimuthal, Mercator, Mollweide, orthographic, and rectangular
projections can be drawn, and clouds can be optionally overlaid.
Visit the homepage http://www.xplanet.sourceforge.net
to get links for cloud maps and planet images.'
